{
  "section_id": "18-why-apple-will-not-build-fabs",
  "title": "Why Apple Will Not Build Fabs",
  "title_translation": "为什么苹果不会自建晶圆厂",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "id": "p000",
      "index": 0,
      "source": "With $200 billion in cash, Apple could theoretically outspend any foundry on earth. Yet, the economics of building a leading-edge fab from scratch are prohibitive even for Cupertino.",
